Package com.SuperheroSightings.springbootrestjdbctemplatemaven.dao

Class OrganizationDAOImpl

java.lang.Object
com.SuperheroSightings.springbootrestjdbctemplatemaven.dao.OrganizationDAOImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
OrganizationDAO
@Repository public class OrganizationDAOImpl extends Object implements OrganizationDAO
Implementation class for data access operations related to the Organization entity. This class provides the actual JDBC implementation for CRUD and other operations defined in the OrganizationDAO interface, making use of the JdbcTemplate for database interactions.
